title.narrative: Savings and Credit Sector Consolidation and Financial Inclusion Project

description.narrative: The objective of the project is to support the: (a) consolidation of the savings and credit sector institutions (SCI); and (b) deepening of financial inclusion in selected areas and selected locations in Mexico.
